ABSORPTION.description:
Increases the maximum health of an entity with health that cannot be
 regenerated, but is refilled every 30 seconds.

BAD_OMEN.description:
Triggers a raid when the player enters a village.
 oof.

CONDUIT_POWER.description: Effects granted by a nearby conduit.

DAMAGE_RESISTANCE.description: Decreases damage dealt to an entity.

DARKNESS.description: Causes the player's vision to dim occasionally.

DOLPHINS_GRACE.description:
Increses underwater movement speed.
 Squee'ek uh'k kk'kkkk squeek eee'eek.

GLOWING.description: Outlines the entity so that it can be seen from afar.

HEALTH_BOOST.description: Increases the maximum health of an entity.

HERO_OF_THE_VILLAGE.description:
Reduces the cost of villager trades.
 \o/.

LEVITATION.description: Causes the entity to float into the air.

NIGHT_VISION.description: Allows an entity to see in the dark.

POISON.description: Deals damage to an entity over time.

SATURATION.description: Increases the food level of an entity each tick.

WEAKNESS.description: Decreases damage dealt by an entity.

WITHER.description:
Deals damage to an entity over time and gives the health to the
 shooter.
